  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You can increase the power of your spells, causing them to deal more damage.</em><br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />All variable, numeric effects of an empowered spell are increased by half including bonuses to those dice rolls.<br /><br />Saving throws and opposed rolls are not affected, nor are spells without random variables. An empowered spell uses up a spell slot two levels higher than the spell's actual level.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Usage</strong>: create copies of spells and adjust them.</p>",
